relation: The Drummer from the Runaway Five Had a bit of trouble uploading this one. Problems on my end. If it turns out I submitted the same thing twice, I apologize.
Seriously, dude, don't ride that bike in a cave.
I went for another realistic-ish approach.
So sharp, you won't feel a thing.

The Dragon Point coin interpretations are back! This time, everything is based off of the American coins. I should point out right now that if anyone feels offended with these, just know that it is not my intention to do so. I'm just doing this for fun and I don't mean for anything to be taken seriously. Fun Fact: As a replacement for "E Pluribus Unum", I had originally thought of putting in "Spankety, Spankety, Spankety", but then, that didn't make me feel very good, at least from a moral standpoint, so I instead settled on another catchy, familiar jingle. Enjoy!
